    "description": "<p>When using this skill, you may spend up to three [Fate Points] (0 is okay). You gain a + [(Spent [Fate Points] + SR) x 5] bonus to [Weapon Attack] damage rolls.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(CR 11): The multiplier bonus becomes x 10. </p>\n<p>(CR 21): The multiplier bonus becomes x 15.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill that allows you to unleash a series of attacks with a dancing movement that even the enemy is amazed by. The path of the weapon shining with blood smoke becomes a dance of death, stealing the life of the enemy with the sword.</p>",
